  <dd>Complete details on the API, the lifecycle of different data objects, project permissions, and more. Many methods in the bindings translate directly into API calls, so it will be helpful to have at least a general understanding of the API's structure.</dd>
  <dt><a class="reference external" href="https://wiki.dnanexus.com/Execution-Environment-Reference">Execution Environment Reference</a></dt>
