<h4>dxcpp provides the following handler classes for DNAnexus objects:</h4>
<ul>
  <li>dx::DXApp</li>
  <li>dx::DXApplet</li>
  <li>dx::DXContainer</li>
  <li>dx::DXFile</li>
  <li>dx::DXGTable</li>
  <li>dx::DXJob</li>
  <li>dx::DXProject</li>
  <li>dx::DXRecord</li>
  <li>dx::DXSystem</li>
</ul>

<h4>The following helpers will provide assistance with interfacing between your
app(let) and the execution environment:</h4>

<ul>
  <li>exec_utils.h</li>
</ul>

<h4>The following classes are used for throwing exceptions (all derive eventually from std::exception):</h4>
<ul>
  <li>dx::DXAPIError</li>
  <li>dx::DXError</li>
  <li>dx::DXFileError</li>
  <li>dx::DXGTableError</li>
  <li>dx::DXNotImplementedError</li>
</ul>

